<HEADLINE> Jianlibao Youth Soccer Team to Play Latvia Dynamo </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NANNING, April 20 (Xinhua) -- The Jianlibao Youth Soccer Team
will play Latvia Dynamo here on May 4, according to the organizers
here on Sunday.
</P>
<P>
The Jianlibao eleven, finishing third at the Nehru Cup soccer
tournament earlier this month, takes the match as a warm-up for
the World Youth Soccer Championships in June in Malaysia. 
</P>
