<HEADLINE> Gujral 3rdadd: Indian President Appoints New PM to </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NEW DELHI, April 20 (Xinhua) -- Indian President Shanker Dayal
Sharma said today that he appointed United Front (UF) leader I. K.
Gujral the country's 12th prime minister in a bid to avert a
mid-term poll in less than a year, the Press Trust of India
reported.
</P>
