partner of the Palestinians and President Yasser Arafat on the
peace process.
</P>
<P>
"(U.S. Middle East peace coordinator Dennis) Ross was here
last week, we didn't get anything going because of what is
happening in Israel now," he said, adding "We think we should, with
the Israelis, go back on the right track of the peace process."
