<TEXT>
<P>
MANILA, April 21 (Xinhua) -- Dr. Nafis Sadik, executive
director of the United Nations Fund for Population Activities
(UNFPA), will pay a visit to the Philippines on April 24-25, the
UNFPA resident representative in Manila said today.
</P>
<P>
