dollars. Rashid Hussain gained 80 cents to end at 10.3 Singapore
dollars, while BerLei Warrant 99, Elec and the Overseas Chinese
Banking Corporation (OCBC) Foreign picked up by 30 cents each to
close at 1.9 Singapore dollars, 5.35 US dollars, and 17.8
Singapore dollars respectively.
