<HEADLINE> Vice-Premier Zou Jiahua Inspects South China Economic Zone </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SHENZHEN, April 21 (Xinhua) -- Vice-Premier Zou Jiahua urged
Shenzhen, the pioneer in China's reform and opening to the outside
world, to speed up development of its information industry, during
a recent visit there.
</P>
<P>
Zou expressed satisfaction with the remarkable achievement in
