</P>
<P>
However, he stressed that Shenzhen should develop its
information industry in accordance with the needs of a market
economy, improve marketing, reduce risks and increase efficiency.
</P>
<P>
Zou visited a number of high-tech enterprises and talked with
managers, technicians, and foreign experts. He also visited local
people and watched as one person demonstrated the use of a
personal computer to handle matters related to work and daily life.
</P>
</TEXT>
