<HEADLINE> Bruguera Wins First Round at Monte Carlo Tennis </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
PARIS, April 21 (Xinhua) -- Sergi Bruguera had a perfect start
at the Monte Carlo tennis Open on Monday, beating compatriot
Spaniard Javier Sanchez in straight sets.
</P>
