<TEXT>
<P>
STOCKHOLM, April 21 (Xinhua) -- Swedish ice hockey star Mats
Sundin announced on Monday that he would not play at the World
Championships in Finland from April 26 to May 14.
</P>
<P>
Sundin, a forward with the Toronto Maple Leafs in the National
