billion US dollars, about five percent up from last year. Its
exports in the first quarter were valued at about 1.3 billion US
dollars, a year-on-year 21.43 percent increase, Liu said, hoping
that the deals agreed during the fair will contribute more to the
fulfillment of the target.
</P>
<P>
The city's industrial structure of overseas-funded enterprises
have been markedly improved in the first quarter. Among the newly
licenced 71 overseas ventures, 53 are engaged in industrial
production projects, Liu said.
